The collection is divided into eight series: Series 1: Administrative Files, 1928-1994; Series
            2: Committee Files, 1958-1991; Series 3: Committee
            Reports, 1955-1992; Series 4: Bulletin, 1942-1996;
            Series 5: Clippings and Miscellaneous Files, 1959-1988;
            Series 6: Oversize, undated;
            Series 7: RFC 1994 75th Anniversary History, 1919-1994; Series
            8: Raymond Pinchbeck Collection of RFC materials, 1948-1998
